net.ljcomputing.fx.control.time

Enum TimeSpinner.Mode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TimeSpinner.Mode>
      • net.ljcomputing.fx.control.time.TimeSpinner.Mode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TimeSpinner.Mode>
    Enclosing class:
    TimeSpinner

    static enum TimeSpinner.Mode
extends Enum<TimeSpinner.Mode>
    Mode represents the unit that is currently being edited. For convenience expose methods for incrementing and decrementing that unit, and for selecting the appropriate portion in a spinner's editor.
